                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140112-86-off445 t18140112-86-cd446"></join>, twenty-three yards of printed cotton, value 25 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18140112-86-victim776" type="victimName">
                     William 
